column5: Well im back in action with the Kings & Brown Trout.. if your looking for some Salmon Action get ahold of me ..
Can I just follow your boat out and see what you are using  See ya next week for some cats!
no need to follow me just ask ..
Steve can't wait to get out!!   now that i gots that walleye itch fixed,,,,TIME FOR THE KINGS!!!   Nice catch as usua!
Those are some nice fish!. I would go but I'm sure my rod couldnt handle one of those Salmon.
